{
  "stem": "20088.7",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Frank and that he had seen my father and Heinz but they had left the camp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But at least we knew they were still alive not too long ago.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we decided, well, there's no point staying there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we'll go back the next day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we took whatever we had taken, our blankets and my boots.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd taken lovely boots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And warm jackets.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had good clothes then, whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we couldn't carry so much, of course, because we were weak.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But whatever we could carry, we took.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we marched back to the men's camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there the Russians didn't really organize anything yet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were still busy getting themselves straight.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I say, the fighting was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there was definitely a center there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they tried to-- the first things they did send was to cut the bunk beds down to single beds so because they realized that it was difficult for people to go up to the top bunk.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they organized people to come and do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said you can go and stay wherever you-- you know, move in wherever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we didn't want to live with the men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So on top of a building there was a little room where we said we are going to live there for the time being.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we put all our things there and we went out again to find things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one day I found a big liver sausage in the street.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And took that to our home and I ate the whole liver sausage.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you can imagine what pain I had and what cramps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I was again in agony and then I decided that I just must not eat so much because it's going to kill my inside.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
